s the old word won&apos;t disappear because <span class=\"tex-span\">10&#x2009;-&#x2009;9&#x2009;&#x2264;&#x2009;1</span>.</p>","sampleTestcases":[{"id":1624134212526,"input":"6 5\n1 3 8 14 19 20\n","output":"3"},{"id":1624134212527,"input":"6 1\n1 3 5 7 9 10\n","output":"2"}],"submitUrl":"https://codeforces.com/contest/716/submit","language":"python"}